ygData.msgSnippet: I can tell EQ is down -- I ll be glad when the game is up and we can all go back to playing rather than arguing about the length of the signatures on peoples
ygData.messageBody:
I can tell EQ is down -- I'll be glad when the game is up and we can all go
back to playing rather than arguing about the length of the signatures on
peoples' e-mail! I for one, had great plans for the day -- instead I had to
spend it doing real-life productive things. What a drag!



----- Original Message -----
From: Beeler <kbeeler@...>
To: <EQCheats@onelist.com>
Sent: Monday, September 13, 1999 2:36 PM
Subject: Re: [EQCheats] Digest Number 129


> From: Beeler <kbeeler@...>
>
> Make that three. although I have a sig, it is by no means large, it is

>

<douglas@...>
